==English==

===Verb===
{{en-verb2|'''to [[fall]] [[in]] [[love]] [[with]]'''|'''[[falls in love with]]'''|'''[[fell in love with]]'''|'''[[fallen in love with]]'''|'''[[falling in love with]]'''}}

# {{transitive}} To come to have feelings of [[romantic love]] towards (someone), or a sense of delight in or great pleasure regarding (something).
#:''I am '''falling in love with''' you.''
#:''I have just '''fallen in love with''' Rome!''

